(35, 1, '2016-04-18 10:33:33', '2016-04-18 10:33:33', 'We are proud of our track record of working with extraordinary scientists, enterpreneurs and buisness leaders to build transformational companies that impact and improve healthcare and big data industries.\r\n<p class="text-uppercase">We invest our time, resources and expertise in all our portfolio partnerships.</p>\r\nWe pursue opportunities where we can add value through our collaborative partership approach, and devote a mix of strategic advice, domain expertise and capital to help the portfolio companies’ growth. Since our inception in 2010, we have invested in 13 early and venture stage companies.', 'Portfolio', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'portfolio', '', '', '2016-04-21 11:05:49', '2016-04-21 11:05:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/langsang/?p=35', 0, 'post', '', 0),
