(169, 1, '2016-04-20 05:12:17', '2016-04-20 05:12:17', '<p style="text-align: left;">上海朗盛投资有限公司（“朗盛”）成立于2010年，是一家重点关注大数据、生命科学等高科技产业的风险投资公司。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">朗盛以资本为纽带为企业成长保驾护航，除了为被投资企业的发展提供创投资金外，朗盛凭借着与本土各级政府部门、各行业优秀企业家、权威专家、各类金融服务机构所建立的良好关系，在拓展商业渠道、吸纳优秀人才、建立现代企业制度、对接战略资源，及后期融资等方面为企业提供专业支持、经验和资源。朗盛目前在管资产 总金额已接近6个亿人民币，已投资了15家大数据及生命科学企业。</p>', '关于我们', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-20 05:12:17', '2016-04-20 05:12:17', '', 33, 'http://localhost/langsang/33-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(170, 1, '2016-04-20 05:13:26', '2016-04-20 05:13:26', '<p style="text-align: left;">Lang Sheng Investment is a leading life science and big data investment firm in China committed to helping exceptional entrepreneurs build the next generation of great healthcare and big data companies.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We invest across the healthcare and big data sectors with an emphasis on the venture stages of company development. With close to RMB600 million under management and the headquarters in Shanghai, Lang Sheng has built a team with strong investment expertise. Since the firm’s founding in 2010, we have invested in 13 companies in the life science and big data companies in China.</p>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '30-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-20 05:13:26', '2016-04-20 05:13:26', '', 30, 'http://localhost/langsang/30-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
